<p style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0.2em;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #1fa39d;" href="http://getinvolved.pogo.org/site/R?i=mplJM9gSNB9ZGXEhDOCYyg"><strong>In Snowden&rsquo;s Wake: New Book Examines Needed Intelligence Reforms</strong></a></p>
<p style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 150%; margin: 0.2em;">Regardless of how you view Edward Snowden, Ronald Goldfarb&rsquo;s new book shows that Snowden&rsquo;s revelations have forever altered America&rsquo;s political landscape. 
<a style="text-decoration: none; color: #1fa39d;" href="http://getinvolved.pogo.org/site/R?i=0Ejgf1pbAxMe3xNdbHhUyA"><strong>Read more</strong></a></p>
